### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ وَأَخْبَتُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِمْ أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ أَصْحَـٰبُ ٱلْجَنَّةِ ۖ هُمْ فِيهَا خَـٰلِدُونَ</span>

### English

Surely those who believe, do good, and humble themselves before their Lord will be the residents of Paradise. They will be there forever.